-Skills in reviewing Change Controls, Stability Protocols, Clinical Trial Protocols, and Packaging Artwork.
-Experience obtaining country-specific variation feedback and managing submission timelines.
-Ability to handle dossier renewals and maintain regulatory records.
-Strong follow-up and documentation tracking skills with cross-functional and manufacturing teams.
-Experience reviewing requirements for upcoming international market filings.
-6–8 years of regulatory affairs experience with international market submissions.
-Strong understanding of CTD, ACTD, eCTD formats and ICH guidelines.

